      "id": "cPaHSS3QEbMXyIcOX43rsa0w2w9jx10umoz",
      "questionNumber": 7,
      "questionText": "The increasing order of nucleophilicity of the following nucleophiles is :\n<br>(a) CH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>2</sub><sup>$$-$$</sup> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b) H<sub>2</sub>O\n<br>(c) CH<sub>3</sub>SO<sub>3</sub><sup>$$-$$</sup> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(d) $$\\mathop O\\limits^ -  H$$",
      "options": [
        "(b) &lt; (c) &lt; (a) &lt; (d)",
